    - Did NOT touch InsightsOrchestrator.cs (035 may also touch it for scope-shape changes — no collision)
    - Touched InsightsModule.cs (035 may also; my changes are additive — new registrations near the existing ILiveFactResolver block, no rewrites of surrounding registrations)
